---
import LogoTemp from '../assets/logo_temp.png';
import LogoIdentite from '../assets/identite.jpg';
import TechCarousel from './TechCarousel.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>ECV - Nathan Fourny</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Section Principale -->
  <main class="home-main">
    <div class="background-image"></div>
    <div class="content-overlay">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h1>Bienvenue sur mon Portfolio</h1>
        <p>
          <br />Je suis Nathan Fourny, développeur en informatique curieux, j'aime explorer les différents domaines de la programmation. Que ce soit dans le développement web, de jeux-vidéos, logiciels ou encore mobile, je m'investis pleinement dans les projets que j'entreprend et aime particulièrement approfondir les différentes notions que je peux découvrir.<br /> Ouvert d'esprit et rigoureux, cette soif de découverte et cette volonté d'apprendre se traduisent aux travers de mes différents projets que je vous invite à explorer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-photo">
        <img src={LogoIdentite.src} alt="Photo de Nathan Fourny" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <TechCarousel />

  <section class="below-carousel">
    <!-- Onglet Projets (gauche) -->
    <div class="projects-box">
      <h2>Mes Projets</h2>
      <p>
        Voici un aperçu de mes projets les plus récents et significatifs. 
        Découvrez comment j'ai mis en pratique mes compétences 
        pour développer des applications, des sites et bien plus encore.
      </p>
      <a href="/projects" class="project-button">
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Onglet Formulaire Contact (droite) -->
    <div id="contact" class="contact-box">
      <h2>Contactez-moi</h2>
      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Nom</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="subject">Objet</label>
          <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required />
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Envoyer</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap');

    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .home-main {
      position: relative;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .background-image {
      background-image: url('../assets/background.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .content-overlay {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      max-width: 1200px;
      width: 90%;
      height: 75%;
    }

    .intro-text {
      flex: 1;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      border-radius: 8px;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .intro-text h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .intro-text p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .profile-photo {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .profile-photo img {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .profile-photo img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .content-overlay {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .intro-text, .profile-photo {
        flex: none;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .profile-photo {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .intro-text h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .intro-text p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .profile-photo img {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
      }
    }

    .below-carousel {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 3rem auto 5rem auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .projects-box {
      flex: 1;
      background-color: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .projects-box h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .projects-box p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .project-button {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 2px solid #fff; 
      color: #fff;
      background: transparent;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    .project-button:hover {
      background: #fff;
      color: #000;
    }
    .arrow {
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .contact-box {
      flex: 1;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #333;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .contact-box h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 4px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .submit-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .submit-button:hover {
      background-color: #333;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .below-carousel {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
